From the bartender to the cook to the owner... All around good vibes. Family/ friendly/ sports oriented, great food, good beer. Would recommend to anyone looking for a true Buffalo pub experience. Today, I stopped in for their homemade and truly original pizza rolls and they were amazing... Crispy and super super fresh. Along with Southern Tier IPA, my pint of choice. Everything was perfect. Definitely, my pit stop for any sports outting, baseball, or hockey especially.

One of the best places to go to when downtown either for lunch, dinner, or any event that is going on! Great service! Great Food! Employees will always go above and beyond to make things right! For example our waiter comped us our drinks because he felt like the food took to long to come out which came out within 15 minutes of us ordering! Staff is amazing! Always a go to in my book!
